IMHO, enterprise integration is actually the same problem space like the one of the Web.

The scale is different, but the complexity issues are pretty much the same.

From a technology investment POV, HTTP will beat any vendor-specific stack any time, especially with regard to protection of investment, quality of products and developer availability.

